    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid leaks and a bit of hesitation during cold starts. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and a few non-functional plastic trim pieces. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
