      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. The S54 3.2L inline-six remains a masterpiece, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline with crisp throttle response via individual throttle bodies. This specimen features a flawless 6-speed manual gearbox and a fully documented service history, including a preventative VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by a limited-slip differential that ensures optimal power distribution. Finished in museum-grade condition with zero bolster wear on the Nappa leather and a pristine undercarriage, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
